Olivia Burnette https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Olivia_Burnette 0 Olivia Nicole Burnette (born March 24, 1977) is an American actress who began her career as a child actress at the age of six. She is perhaps best known for her role in the NBC sitcom The Torkelsons (1991–1993). Burnette was nominated for eleven Young Artist Award.
